-<p><a name="st_79"></a>
-<a name="07030520000011"></a><b><a name="70305-0006.htm_spnew1"></a><a name="07030520000396"></a>Baroness Scotland of Asthal:</b> My Lords, I beg the noble Lord&#146;s pardon. He will know that a decision was also made in the Supreme Court on Friday. Whether the special advocate should have additional issues is a matter of some interest. Of course we will look at that and take it into consideration. It is perhaps important to acknowledge that there is an implicit acceptance that the special advocate procedure might have a certain degree of utility and support.</p>
