+<p><a name="stpa_163"></a><a name="07030520000095"></a>This is a short, straightforward and functional Bill which has nothing to say about the policy, nature or operation of a planning-gain supplement. It has been introduced to ensure the regularity and propriety of government expenditure in line with government accounting rules.</p>
 
