+<ul><a name="07030511000429"></a>
+<p><a name="wa_qnpa_3"></a>Which authority is responsible for the provision of accommodation for United Nations troops in the Ledra Palace, Nicosia; and which public bodies finance the provision of this accommodation. [HL2184]</p>
